{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo is an early build, if you are interested in playing the Wind's Path early. Any feedback would be appreciated. The full game is set for March 2025. So please let me know if you find any bugs or have any other issues with the game. I'll do my best to fix them if I can!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">This demo includes, two completely playable levels and boss fights. There's no story cutscenes included in this demo, maybe in future builds. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">The Wind's Path is a top down platformer.</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/Olis_looking_at_Astral_Plane_Darker_BG_AND_STARS.png?t=1738751195\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">You've been granted the power to control the wind!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/Olis_Receive_Wind_Powers__small_.png?t=1738751195\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Your wind powers are fueled by the &quot;Flow&quot; meter.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/Flow_Meter_-_No_BG_no_decrease.gif?t=1738751195\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/movement_video_2.gif?t=1738751195\" /></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> Unlock various wind powers!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/Wind_Powers_Video.gif?t=1738751195\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0\u00a0\u00a0\u00a0 \u00a0 \u00a0 </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Dodge attacks and defeat dangerous enemies to increase Flow.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/Wind_Shield.png?t=1738751195\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Travel from world to world to recover reality altering shards!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/extras/Rue_Looking_at_Shards_2_small.png?t=1738751195\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1738751195","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/page.bg.jpg?t=1738751195","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/5b31f5a0f9fe7de776bc56f8ada66ff5d56fac54/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1738751195","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3114920/5b31f5a0f9fe7de776bc56f8ada66ff5d56fac54/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1738751195","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10},{"description":"Steam Achieveme